    <p>Our purpose is to enable parents and child care service providers to connect to a local network of parents and providers for the purpose of coordinating with one another on matters pertaining to child care.</p>

    <p>Users may create events pertaining to child care, browse events created by other users, send messages to other users, and sign up for posted events.</p>

    <div id="sign-up-in">
        <%= link_to 'Register', new_user_registration_path %>   - or -   <%= link_to 'Sign in', new_user_session_path %>
    </div>
    <img src="assets/children_all_ages.jpg">
